ouncil's services and opening days/times over the Christmas period. <a data-cms-link-uri=\"articles/1709\" href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/pages/council_services_over_christmas\">Full details</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"content\"><div class=\"frame\"><div id='app_content'><div id=\"my-location\"><div class='module location-details'><div class='header'><h2>My Location</h2></div><div class='body'><p class=\"address\">Your location is: <strong>1A, High Meadow, Hathern</strong>. <a class=\"edit-location\" href=\"location?delete&amp;redirect=/\">Change to a different location</a>.</p>\n</div></div><div class='row'><div class='col col-property'><div class=\"module refusecollectiondates\">\n<div class=\"header\"><h3 class=\"title\">Refuse Collection Dates</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"body\"><ul class=\"refuse\"><li class=\" first\"><strong class=\"date\">Tue 30th Dec</strong><a class=\"refuse\" href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/pages/refusecollectionservice\">Refuse</a></li><li><strong class=\"date\">Mon 5th Jan</strong><a class=\"gardenwaste\" href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/pages/garden_waste\">Garden Waste</a></li><li class=\" last\"><strong class=\"date\">Tue 6th Jan</strong><a class=\"recycling\" href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/pages/recycling_information\">Recycling</a></li></ul>\n<div class=\"refuse-note alert\"><p>There are changes to waste collections over the festive period. For more information, <a href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/pages/christmas_waste_collection\">visit the Christmas waste collections webpage</a>.</p>\n<p>Please be aware there will be no garden waste collections for the weeks commencing&#160;Monday, 22 December and&#160;Monday, 29 December 2025. The service will resume from&#160;Monday, 5 January 2026. This means the final garden waste collections of 2025 will take place the week commencing&#160;Monday, 15 December 2025.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"footer empty\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"module ctband\"><h3>Council Tax</h3><div class=\"body\"><p class=\"ctband\">Your property is in <strong><a class=\"more\" rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/ctbands\">Council Tax Band D</a></strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.charnwood.gov.uk/ctbands\">Your annual Council Tax amount can be found here</a>.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"module propertyattributes\"><h3>Property Notices</h3><div class='body'><ul class=\"propertyattributes\"><li class=\"enfnot... [truncated]",
